Enclosing class:
HTMLNode
public static class HTMLNode.HTMLDoctype
extends HTMLNode

Special HTML node for the DOCTYPE declaration. This node differs from a normal HTML node in that it's child (and it should only have exactly one child, the "html" node) is rendered after this node.
